{"tid":1014482,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(真人真事)啲蝗客真係特別戇鳩","createTime":"2019-02-09T08:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T13:19:51.000Z","uid":106001,"like":71,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab3c4e121d546eaa0cc9929fd8750d14b25059c","tid":1014482,"uid":106001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T08:31:43.000Z","msg":"Part time做緊某旅遊景點嘅店員<br />\n因為啲貨係喺個櫃入面<br />\n客人唔可以自己拎<br />\n所以平時客人要啲乜我就幫佢拎<br />\n今日有一家3蝗入左黎<br />\n蝗老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝗老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝗仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：你要什麼？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 指一指後面蝗仔：問小孩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：這個4個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：2個啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：4個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：2個<br />\n如是者loop咗幾次我最後聽老母講拎咗2個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：再給我來個這個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：不要<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：不要？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：不要<br />\n我：你們先想好<br />\n跟住我將佢堆野放喺一邊<br />\n經理行過見到屌鳩我：呢堆野做乜架？邊個架跟埋佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我嗰時已經燥燥地<br />\n我：佢地未諗好wor後面成堆人<br />\n經理：跟埋先跟後面啦<br />\n我廢事嘈繼續問蝗老母到底要唔要<br />\n佢話唔要<br />\n跟住行去收銀處<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：還是要啦<br />\n跟住我又行返去拎俾佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尖叫：不要<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：好啦不要不要<br />\n我真係頂唔撚順<br />\n用個偏大嘅聲量自言自語：屌你老母啲大陸人戇鳩鳩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n經理：喂____你講咩呀<br />\n我：我話嗰2個大陸人戇鳩鳩呀又話要又唔要想點呀？後面成堆人排緊隊<br />\n經理：你做咩講粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：講咪講囉<br />\n經理呆撚咗：你講咩話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：大陸人都聽唔明架啦<br />\n經理：都唔可以喺客人面前咁鬧佢地架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係忍唔撚住屌埋經理：屌~講真你地自己平時都細細聲屌鳩啲大陸客啦~又要屌又要細聲<br />\n經理唔知點答：都唔可以咁架wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔理佢繼續做其他野<br />\n佢都冇再出聲繼續做返自己野<br />\n跟住突然有個同事走黎叫我收得工<br />\n我走嗰時同經理講返埋呢兩日唔返<br />\n講真面對啲大陸閪客真係唔洗同佢客氣<br />\n特別是你係part time<br />\n咁嘅情況個經理仲屌鳩你呢啲工真係唔休做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真人真事講大話過唔到2019投胎做中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db4e3ec69a366908b2bf4fea2dde8392903caa5","tid":1014482,"uid":68598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T08:33:07.000Z","msg":"開名等人唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f3891da2d47c3e9fec36bd39fcba925b453af0","tid":1014482,"uid":141500,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T08:34:05.000Z","msg":"經理係咪新移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684a2bff4b0edc0d0697d025d686c184cecd6010","tid":1014482,"uid":156681,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T08:37:09.000Z","msg":"個經理都係戇鳩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336b20038268efa880531bd78ace198a1e58988a","tid":1014482,"uid":26197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T08:38:52.000Z","msg":"360?"},{"pid":"3dceeec152661280c4c5cc56137c8985be5eb790","tid":1014482,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-