lyTime":"2019-02-09T09:14:15.000Z","msg":"名就唔開啦<br />\n因為我覺得好多遊客區服務業都有呢啲情況<br />\n大家唔好話貪佢高少少人工就走去做<br />\n有時啲蝗客閪起上黎都幾惡做"},{"pid":"4cf9c2dcca102b33122b54d27a78402099abfcdb","tid":1014482,"uid":46901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:17:25.000Z","msg":"海洋公園/迪士尼係多大陸狗架啦 係我就當面用普通話屌柒佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f82709c7f81a967328285197cb98654a97d582","tid":1014482,"uid":106001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cf9c2dcca102b33122b54d27a78402099abfcdb","tid":1014482,"uid":46901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:17:25.000Z","msg":"海洋公園/迪士尼係多大陸狗架啦 係我就當面用普通話屌柒佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:19:01.000Z","msg":"巴打有啲經歷咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462ee6576a52808b37abed8807202c7eca764b44","tid":1014482,"uid":106001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb98f3c0e606937b8f8ad5ab975371852b96687d","tid":1014482,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:32:58.000Z","msg":"就咁睇間公司仲西過大陸人喎"},{"pid":"1ca0cebbb437458baac306ead9d7a6260146fd2b","tid":1014482,"uid":106001,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bb98f3c0e606937b8f8ad5ab975371852b96687d","tid":1014482,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:32:58.000Z","msg":"就咁睇間公司仲西過大陸人喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:44:24.000Z","msg":"經理自己平時都會屌鳩啲客<br />\n雖然我認我咁大聲係大膽咗啲<br />\n但佢其身不正都屌鳩我鬧啲客我覺得佢戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f707dcd00860ce71b2a35eb07602e2218ceb7b2","tid":1014482,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ca0cebbb437458baac306ead9d